 Just think of it! They've won lowering of customs duties and now started knocking great expansion in investment spending out of WTO for own producers' supporting! Joining the ranks of other US vassals such as Poland, Lithuania, Estonia, Latvia and Georgia and hoping in all-round support of its overseas friends, Kiev is under the impression that it gets what ever it wants in WTO! 
 And after it we dare to nibble at US offer about Ukraine's joining NATO? Idiocy!
